title: Strange event, Everyone dies - ever happened to you ?

embed.description: Everyone dies, the map is deserted. Very rare moment.

replies.body: Happened a few times for me in ARAM. Always fun, especially late game when timers are long. Just the game playing itself.
its only happened to me twice in 4 years of playing.
It's not that crazy. Everybody will just be shopping and yelling about who to focus for the next 30 seconds or whatever.
